CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: ImageneBio is a clinical-stage biotechnology company that boldly imagines a world where patients can be free from the burden of grievous immunological/autoimmune and inflammatory ('I&I') diseases. Imagene's purpose is to globally develop new medicines with differentiated profiles that can effectively control and change the course of I&I diseases for affected patients, treat their symptoms, and improve quality of life.
